class BodyRightBreadcrumTemplate extends MasterTemplate {

	_viewClassName = 'BodyRightTemplateBreadcrumView';

	onListen : function () {
		var dispatcher = _super();

		dispatcher.listen('History:change:url', this, this.reload);

		return dispatcher;
	}

	reload : function () {
		this._view.reload();
	}

	getLinks : function () {
		var links = [];
		var path = window.location.pathname.toString().substr(1).split('/');
		var len = path.length;
		var link = '';
		var elem = {};

		for (var i = 0; i < len; ++i) {
			link += '/'+ path[i];
			elem = {};
			elem['name'] = path[i].toUpperCase();
			elem['link'] = link;
			links.push(elem);
		}
		return links;
	}

}